List ToDo

The [prgm]todo[/prgm] command lists ToDo entries found in [bold]ToDo.md[/bold] files in child directories.

Files in directories containing [arg-value]_archived[/arg-value] in their path are automatically skipped.

$ [prgm]todo list[/prgm]         # List todo entries
$ [prgm]todo edit[/prgm] [arg-value]project[/arg-value]  # Open a project's ToDo file in the editor
